channel.title: Torvapkz V1-3 - Finally here! - over 100k views, thank you!
channel.description:
enjoy ;) this is teamtorva the v3 [size=18pt][b]source and client link [/b] [/size] - http://uppit.com/sx19gebhpe7x/Teamtorva_package.rar - Resposted as a 100k views celebration :) thank you!
Guys i know i promised a 317 with 642 items so here it is it has taken me about a month and a half because i had school but now its summer time so it will not be very long until i can release v2 but as for version 1 here it is and enjoy but first read the things i have added to the server:
and torvapkz version2 is now out :) [size=36pt]version 2[/size] has so much more to offer including well just about everything!!!!! version 2 download link: http://uppit.com/jrnx1ni1owuo/Torvapkz_source_v2.rar [size=36pt][font=arial]Torvapkz[/font][/size] [IMG]http://i1229.photobucket.com/albums/ee464/austin1234able/Torvapkz/frosties.png[/img] [IMG]http://i1229.photobucket.com/albums/ee464/austin1234able/Torvapkz/donatorchest.png[/img] added korasi's sword special attack working 100% [IMG]http://i1229.photobucket.com/albums/ee464/austin1234able/Torvapkz/100clanchat-1.png[/img] added in-game high-scores so you can beat your friend's ;) made torva give +25 strength bonus rather than +7 and +25 prayer bonus made chaotic rapier give +105 str bonus rather than +101 and a +5 prayer bonus made chaotic maul give a +7 prayer bonus and a +165 str bonus rather than +155 fixed corporeal glitch, you fight him correctly now. [IMG]http://i1229.photobucket.com/albums/ee464/austin1234able/Torvapkz/100clanchat.png[/img] jad glitch's fixed, added a new donator store for donators, added summoning. working turmoil and other curses 100%, working pvp combat 100%. working slayer tasks 95% complete (should be 100 in v2). full working vengeance, in version 2 i am adding completionist cape with emote. completionist cape will give +8 strength bonus :). made clan chat work 100% no bugs, fixed xp counter glitch's, All fixed! :) made you start out with 5m cash, so you can buy stuff that you want. jad glitch is now fixed he won't disapear when you try to fight him anymore.\ added dungeoneering interface in beta currently, added a ::restart command so when you get done compiling you can simply type ::restart to exit server and reboot by itself so you wont have to do all that extra clicking. :) added ::shop 1 which brings up the i buy anything shop interface :). i made jad easier to kill so you can get that firecape! :) added ::copy (username) so you can copy what your friend's look like and ::xcopy (username) so you can make your friend's look just like you, and the best part is it doesn't level their combat stats so they can be a skiller with say torva ;). lowered the cost of chaotic's in the tpk shop to only 325, which probrobly wouldn't even take an hour ;). More to come in version two. pics: [IMG]http://i1229.photobucket.com/albums/ee464/austin1234able/Torvapkz/in-gamehighscoressystem.png[/img] [IMG]http://i1229.photobucket.com/albums/ee464/austin1234able/Torvapkz/fullyworkingsummoning.png[/img] Credits: [size=18pt]Me[/size] 35% for fixing a lot, adding new things and more. xxifish i x 10% for coding a lot in adding new gfx's and more!. [size=18pt]LOVEANDPOWER[/size] for making final judgement base 55%
Update: Fixed Credits ;)
